track_notes: Parking for a car or two without blocking passing place, near Maesnant centre by stream crossing. Follow stream up to right of Pumlumon Fach. At the turn head to right and soon you will be at the summit.

Total time (including ops): 2hr 50m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
